  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857480/extras/9082feddf499c58a7af635d238f9f5c0.webp?t=1654856984\" width=540 height=56 /></span><br>It is a first-person game that uses a keyboard and mouse.<br>You have to approach the enemy's field of view. After succeeding in capturing the enemy, cleanse through consciousness.<br>Attract enemies using ropes to drag them, or show your appearance to attract the enemy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857480/extras/0c55dc7fb952329ce7f6218b53caf680.webp?t=1654856984\" width=540 height=56 /></span><br>*Binding yourself or someone else is dangerous. <br> Do not follow the game if you find a patient who is crazy in the real world.<br> For your safety, do not play this game if you are a minor.<br>*All characters are over the age of 18",
